This template should never be used in articles to link the [[IMDb|Internet Movie Database]], instead use one of the more specific templates listed below.

==Internet Movie Database templates==
*{{tlx|IMDb name}} for people
:*{{tlx|IMDb name}} with the ''|section=bio'' parameter for biographies <!-- deprecating {{IMDb bio}} -->
:*{{tlx|IMDb name}} with the ''|section=awards'' parameter for the awards given to an individual
*{{tlx|IMDb title}} for films, television series, etc.
*{{tlx|IMDb episode}} television series episodes
*{{tlx|IMDb episodes}} for episode lists
*{{tlx|IMDb company}} for companies
*{{tlx|IMDb character}} for fictional characters
*{{tlx|IMDb award}} for events and their associated awards